{{Top|leg}}
The '''Theory of Universal Reference''' stated that time and space were unified and objects could not travel at the speed of light.

It was developed by the [[Drall/Legends|Drall]] [[Scientist/Legends|scientist]] [[Tiran]] circa [[35,000 BBY]].

==Behind the scenes==
The Theory of Universal Reference is equivalent in its fundamental aspects to the [[Wikipedia:theory of relativity|theory of relativity]]. The term "relativity" also exists in the Star Wars universe, as in the case of [[relativistic shield]]ing.

